{"tid":2258823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智利光復成功？","createTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T06:58:48.000Z","uid":369591,"like":79,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"5313d8c2402e681f71e9279517f46abfdc039ed3","tid":2258823,"uid":369591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"智利修憲公投，在已點算的五成投票，近八成民眾支持取代前獨裁者皮諾切特時期制定的憲法。<br />\n<br />\n在公投結束後不久，首都聖地牙哥已經有民眾慶祝，汽車在市中心巡遊響號，著名景點大聖地牙哥通訊塔亮起「重生」的字句。<br />\n<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556668-20201026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556668-20201026.htm&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=152abb5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556668-20201026.htm&h=496aba88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556668-20201026.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋呢個公投政策係比起我地用更加多嘅血肉先換到返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港會唔會都有好似佢哋咁慶祝嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/souguereira/status/1320567944154390528?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsouguereira%2Fstatus%2F1320567944154390528%3Fs%3D21&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=229d167e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsouguereira%2Fstatus%2F1320567944154390528%3Fs%3D21&h=80550d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/souguereira/status/1320567944154390528?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"3ac5983bcb49bc861c9625f9540d29dd4c33e4bf","tid":2258823,"uid":40267,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:40:54.000Z","msg":"民主化左咁耐依加先修憲"},{"pid":"a2e4c3d652e506eb74f6e636566e32c267076493","tid":2258823,"uid":284432